A '''shiv''' was a [[Knife/Legends|knife]] used by many [[Species/Legends|species]]. It was considered just a step above a [[flint knife]]. It consisted of a sharpened blade, usually of metal, that had no other properties, such as a [[Vibro-shiv/Legends|vibro-shiv]] would. [[Kateo]] killed a squad of [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] soldiers with a shiv.

